text: Monika Linkytė (born 3 June 1992) is a Lithuanian singer who has represented Lithuania in the Eurovision Song Contest several times. She took part in the selection for the Lithuanian entry for the Junior Eurovision Song Contest 2007 but did not succeed. Linkytė first represented Lithuania in 2015, where she finished 18th. She returned in 2023, where she finished 11th. Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Lithuanian musicians Category:Singers Category:Eurovision Song Contest entrants
